TITLE

     Rashumon - New student's version

VERSION

    Release 3.0 (25 May 94)

COMPANY

     HarmonySoft - Creative Software for Creative People
     Address: 69 Jabotinsky st. Givatayim 53319 ISRAEL
     Telefax: + 972 3 315 967
     Contact person: Natalia Re'em.

AUTHOR

     Michael Haephrati      Email: harmony@ccsg.tau.ac.il

DESCRIPTION

     Multi-lingual graphic word processor.  Supports languages
     written from right to left as well as left to right.  Can be
     used as a regular graphic word processor as well.  Supports
     graphics import and export, importing files from Mac and PC as
     well as exporting, High quality printing, and a table generator.
     
          *** Technical support using Internet ***

NEW FEATURES

     *	Full Postscript level 2 support (including 1.6m color and gray  
     	scale support.

     *	You can change selection's text size to any size without 
     	effecting the fonts it contains.

     *	You can change selection's fonts to a certain font without 
     	effecting character's sizes.

SPECIAL REQUIREMENTS

     Requires an Amiga with OS compatible with Workbench
     2.04 and a harddisk.

PRICE

     New price: $60.
     "Try and Buy" - you pay $26 (refundable) and try Rashumon for 4 
     weeks. If you want it you add $34 or you return it and get you $26 back.

